on how hard I worked and the accomplishments from hard work.
[AI] 关于我工作的努力程度和努力所取得的成就。

178
00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:02.116
My priorities were completely out of order.
[AI] 我的优先次序完全乱了。

179
00:10:02.140 --> 00:10:03.740
I neglected my family.
[AI] 我忽视了我的家人。

180
00:10:04.820 --> 00:10:06.236
My father had passed away.
[AI] 我父亲去世了。

181
00:10:06.260 --> 00:10:09.060
